reviews.text: Service was good, coffee was good, atmosphere was pleasant. Nice place to sit down for a coffee and a light meal that's close enough to the shops but far enough that you can get away from the crowds for a little.
Very impressed with the coffee and the food at Pause It. Small establishment but very fresh and clean interior, plus a great healthy menu.
Decent coffee. No wifi available and a bit loud though.
Nice looking place with great coffe en food. Egg Benedict and chicken wings where great and the coffees very good. And they use the brand oatley as oat milk which is the best.

Nice cafe settles at the place few steps away from busy tourist and business area. Good for coffee and snacks, hang around with friends and a break to recharge then back to shopping battlefield. They serve wester dishes like salad, pasta, risotto, and for a group of four or six. This place is enough a big group like 20 but better book in advance.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角山東街84號
result.name: Pause It

reviews.text:
小店總有特別的風格和食物 所有我挻喜歡去
這間已去過好幾次 這次和靜靜媽來食東西
去到的時間已經爆場了 等了一會兒就有位坐

·甜睡花果茶 HKD$40
花茶令人放鬆心情 沒有糖分飲到茶的原味道
這個花茶挻清新的味道 挻喜歡這個口感🤭

·菠蘿特飲 HKD$36 
微微的酸酸甜甜 而且顏色挻漸變色的模樣~
夏天飲這個挻生津解渴 可以再來一杯🤤🤤

·凱撒沙律 HKDHKD$48
夏天沒什麼胃口食東西 所以沙律也是不錯的選擇
配上脆脆的面包粒來增加口感 生色不小呢~

·水牛城雞翼 HKD$62
這個口味絕對是一試難忘 食過一次之後
見到那間餐廳有就會叫一份 這間的味道也不錯

小店的招呼挻不錯 所以吸引到很多人來打卡
簡約的小清新風格 已經令人感到很舒服[愉快]
班尼蛋+三文魚$78,雜菇炒蒜意大利粉只有辣味，實在沒有想像中好吃，星期六下午去吃店內都很吵，而且飲品另外叫沒有套餐，吃下來有點貴不值得。
食物新鮮，咖啡好味，可惜舖面太细
裝飾是很好， 優雅， 簡潔， 现代。 如果裝修能夠加入一些吸音設計會更好。

Service was good, coffee was good, atmosphere was pleasant. Nice place to sit down for a coffee and a light meal that's close enough to the shops but far enough that you can get away from the crowds for a little.
